312
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,120
Prosperity for everyone.

313
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:29,960
The history of world finance
is re-written.

314
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:32,040
A few months ago,
no-one would have believed

315
