each German employee could have stock.

316
00:28:36,560 --> 00:28:37,880
Our fund is banking on growth.

317
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:40,280
Particularly for large-scale investors
like you.

318
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:44,320
