321
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:53,880
BUSINESS STATISTICS

322
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:57,080
45 million American dollars.

323
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:06,960
The economy is growing.

324
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,160
It's going uphill all the time.

325
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:11,760
Prosperity for everyone.

326
00:29:13,080 --> 00:29:14,440
Do you believe that?

327
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,280
