337
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:48,680
That's when you want to do and achieve
a lot very fast at the same time.

338
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:50,880
Off the cuff,
without practice or skills.

339
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:53,320
You could say megalomaniac.

340
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:55,840
