of the large banks.

359
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:11,120
I want to know if the small investors
really all fall for this scam and...

360
00:31:12,560 --> 00:31:14,960
And how much they actually know
about this.

361
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:20,360
