Wegener.

364
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:33,960
The mail!

365
00:31:38,320 --> 00:31:39,800
-Hello.
-Hello.

366
00:31:41,800 --> 00:31:42,800
Curtains.

367
00:31:44,280 --> 00:31:45,280
It's heavy.

368
00:31:45,360 --> 00:31:46,960
Here, let me help you.

369
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:58,840
Thank you.

370
00:31:58,920 --> 00:31:59,920
You're welcome.

371
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:03,640
-Ok. Bye.
-Bye.

372
00:32:32,560 --> 00:32:36,200
First he acts all friendly
and gives me a "you'll be fine" look,

373
00:32:36,280 --> 00:32:37,840
