00:35:06,680 --> 00:35:08,040
How did this happen?

408
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:10,920
Someone tampered with the water pipe.

409
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:12,800
It was a proper explosion.

410
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:15,200
