-No.

411
00:35:16,040 --> 00:35:17,440
Who would have done that?

412
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:19,400
I don't know yet.

413
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:23,120
There's more bad news.

414
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:26,920
Betty Winter.

415
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:29,000
No accident, either.

416
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:31,400
What makes you say that?

417
00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:35,320
I tidied the place
before the cops arrived.

418
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:37,120
The spotlight had been tampered with.

419
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,720
-Who knows about this?
-No-one...

420
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:42,120
...saw anything.

421
00:35:43,600 --> 00:35:45,720
-No-one.
-Is that clear?

422
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:54,920
Sawed through?

423
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:59,640
Walter, there was something fishy
about the production from the start.

424
00:36:00,560 --> 00:36:03,320
Right away, a fire in props storage.

425
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:06,440
