455
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:32,200
No. We'll inject a mouse
with your sample.

456
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:35,760
If there is chorionic gonadotropin
in your urine,

457
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:40,400
