466
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:59,800
Oh, him. Yes, just now.

467
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:01,080
Just now?

468
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:03,120
He's supposed to be out by seven.

469
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:06,320
He's got the day, we have the night.
It's in the lease.

470
00:40:08,720 --> 00:40:10,200
It's nearly eight now.

471
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:12,160
You can discuss it with the man himself.

472
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:13,920
But I don't know him.

473
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:16,160
What? Still haven't seen
your fellow tenant?

474
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:17,880
Not so far, no.

475
00:40:19,640 --> 00:40:20,960
Give it to me, moron.

476
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,480
There you are.

477
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:26,000
Come on.

478
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:46,240
Oh, he's left a mess again, that idiot.

479
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:51,040
Typical.

480
00:40:51,120 --> 00:40:53,200
Just drops everything.

481
00:40:55,320 --> 00:40:56,320
Alright.

482
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:01,560
